{"tid":1565024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[跳閘守護隊] 點解藍絲守住閘機，我地唔可以？","createTime":"2019-09-13T03:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T06:21:38.000Z","uid":123933,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9c076615ae5ebf8975764c7d0a29c654b747ebb6","tid":1565024,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:45:52.000Z","msg":"召喚無野做，退休，失業，放假嘅咁多位巴絲，<br />\n得閒就落樓下地鐵站閘機守住，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">隨時準備保護跳閘手足</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">擋一擋，拉一拉，就可以俾到手足跑走，唔使俾mtr / 便衣狗 / 藍絲捉住</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4cb33a6c1f9bbe84f98a2f93f59767b7455c9fae","tid":1565024,"uid":123933,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:47:18.000Z","msg":"每人係閘機守15分鐘<br />\n平時約人地鐵站等，特登早15分鐘到去閘機stand by<br />\n<br />\n每人都咁做，跳閘手足就會安全好多！<br />\n就算你唔敢跳，都可以幫手助工架<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e99065027f3dc68f4eac15147b2d77f4b350d1","tid":1565024,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個都唔知有咩行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔對得住烈士同被捕手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期五 <span style=\"color: red;\">獅子山之路</span> 7:30 樂富 <br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9KQxrNJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?